Python 2.7.x needed
Module needed: poster

To install poster using easy_install or pip:

------------------------------
$ easy_install poster
        [or]
$ pip install poster
------------------------------

If neither easy_install nor pip is available, you need to install distribute first.

------------------------------
$ sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
        [or]
$ curl -O http://python-distribute.org/distribute_setup.py
$ python distribute_setup.py
------------------------------
